Slidenav

What the project is for
	Responsive Bootstrap dropdown slide animation effects plugin
	
How to configure and install it
	Markup
		Note: Include required CSS and JS in correct order
		1. Add slide animation class of choice to "dropdown"
			"jq-slide" and "jqui-slide" for jquery and jqueryui slide effects respectively
		2. Wrap "dropdown-menu" with a div
	JavaScript
		3. Add slide animation script to your JavaScript
		
An example of how to use it or get it running
	Extract files for example/examples
	
The license that the project is offered under
	The MIT License
	
How to contribute to it
	If bug/bugs found, open an issue
	Contact author @ https://gitter.im/tightcode
	
